{"tid":2286207,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂的《Game＆Watch：Super Mario Bros.》在正式發布之前就已經遭到黑客攻擊，可以運行自定義軟件","createTime":"2020-11-14T19:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T03:51:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3a64b1bfb1babc74530958b3c20e102bcec02c","tid":2286207,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:39:14.000Z","msg":"來自德國的安全研究員兼顧問Thomas Roth在11月13日發布的前一天收到了《 Game＆Watch：Super Mario Bros.》，並迅速著手將其拆散。<br />\n<br />\nRoth用化名StackSmashing運營著一個受歡迎的YouTube頻道，致力於規避過去任天堂便攜式設備的安全性，包括破解原始Game Boy的墨盒保護裝置。<br />\n<br />\n在研究了新的Game＆Watch內部組件六個小時之後，Roth聲稱繞過了其安全性，並用修改後的設備替換了該設備的默認Super Mario Bros. ROM。<br />\n<br />\nRoth聲稱該過程不需要焊接，並說他很快將發布一段詳細介紹整個過程的視頻。他沒有說修改是否可能使Game＆Watch運行Super Mario Bros以外的遊戲ROM。"},{"pid":"ceea09ad026f3e93f950102cafa152b0f56c7cb5","tid":2286207,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cdcb31d90f9e54f2eafaf0318b2352d88bf05b5","tid":2286207,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceea09ad026f3e93f950102cafa152b0f56c7cb5","tid":2286207,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:47:52.000Z","msg":"Game&amp;watch lcd game 未聽過？"},{"pid":"f123655c68e74cddb1ce995e9985ab08baf1c1fb","tid":2286207,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceea09ad026f3e93f950102cafa152b0f56c7cb5","tid":2286207,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Gmv5XUQ1ARaxGQCjUIdXfIg9CKU=/1400x1400/filters:format(jpeg)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22031967/GameWatchSuperMarioBros_photo_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FGmv5XUQ1ARaxGQC